paragraphs.text:
val RP = sqlc.sql("select price,formatPRICE from selectGoingPrice where codeNum = " + "\""+ codeNum +"\"order by DATE DESC, TIME DESC limit 1")

val PP = sqlc.sql("select price,formatPRICE from selectGoingPrice where codeNum =" + "\""+ codeNum +"\" AND strDate = \"20171107\" order by TIME DESC limit 1")
val PSP = sqlc.sql("select formatPRICE from selectGoingPrice where codeNum =" + "\""+ codeNum +"\" AND strDate = \"20171107\" order by TIME limit 1")
val PMP = sqlc.sql("select MAX,MIN from selectGoingPriceMM where codeNum =" + "\""+ codeNum +"\" ")
    
val PPP = sqlc.sql("select formatPRICE from selectGoingPrice where codeNum =" + "\""+ codeNum +"\" AND strDate = \"20171106\" order by TIME DESC limit 1")

val mm = sqlc.sql("select * from selectClosingPriceMaxMin where codeNum ="+ "\""+ codeNum +"\"")

val iRecent = RP.select("price").first().getInt(0)
val iPast = PP.select("price").first().getInt(0)

val strRecent = RP.select("formatPRICE").first().getString(0)

val strPastThePast = PPP.select("formatPRICE").first().getString(0)
val strPastStart =  PSP.select("formatPRICE").first().getString(0)
val strPast = PP.select("formatPRICE").first().getString(0)
val strPastMax = PMP.select("MAX").first().getString(0)
val strPastMin = PMP.select("MIN").first().getString(0)

val strMax = mm.select("MAX").first().getString(0)
val strMin = mm.select("MIN").first().getString(0)
val strMaxDate = mm.select("maxDATE").first().getDate(0)
val strMinDate = mm.select("minDATE").first().getDate(0)

val dif = iRecent - iPast

val difSign = 
    if (dif > 0) {
        "▲ "
    } else if ( dif == 0 ) {
        "- "
    } else
        "▼ "

val difColor = 
    if (dif >= 0) { 
        "RED"
    } else 
        "GREEN"
